      "name": "Professional Dental Care",
      "code": "PX081302",
      "abbreviation": "PX081302",
      "description": "Interviewer-administered questions for adults to determine when the participant last visited the dentist and the purpose of the visit. These questions may also be administered to an adult as a proxy for a child.",
